WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.800
The package hub confirms that the service is ready.

00:05.800 --> 00:09.800
The customer enters the store and browses the catalog.

00:09.800 --> 00:16.200
A product is selected and added to the cart.

00:16.200 --> 00:23.600
The synthetic checkout ends with a completed order.

00:23.600 --> 00:32.000
The operator picks up the completed order and reviews its status.

00:32.000 --> 00:39.680
The order and its connected delivery finish successfully.
